						<div class="postbody">It's not lack of fusemap space (which is what you could free up by ditching 4.5×), it's lack of RAM internal to the FPGA.<br /><br />Please review <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=165032#p165032" class="postlink">Tepples's explanation</a>.</div>

